abstract: The author of “Clockers” and, as Harry Brandt, “The Whites” regrets reading “Sophie’s Choice” in 1982: “Never ever read a powerful novel when you’re trying to write a novel of your own.”

abstract: Artisans from “The Grand Budapest Hotel,” “Foxcatcher” and “Guardians of the Galaxy” talk about their challenges and the solutions they came up with.
snippet: Artisans from “The Grand Budapest Hotel,” “Foxcatcher” and “Guardians of the Galaxy” talk about their challenges and the solutions they came up with.
lead_paragraph: Sometimes a well-placed prosthetic or a stylish mustache are just what an audience needs to buy into a story, as evidenced by this year’s Oscar nominees for makeup and hairstyling:  “The Grand Budapest Hotel,” “Foxcatcher” and “Guardians of the Galaxy.”

abstract: NBC’s star-studded three-and-a-half-hour tribute to “Saturday Night Live” was a mostly satisfying blend of self-congratulation and self-mockery.
snippet: NBC’s star-studded three-and-a-half-hour tribute to “Saturday Night Live” was a mostly satisfying blend of self-congratulation and self-mockery.
lead_paragraph: Humor, like beauty, doesn’t always last. Chevy Chase and Eddie Murphy proved that.

abstract: For the 12 years that George Bush held national elective office, Jeb Bush used his unique access to seek favors and make suggestions, helping bolster his own nascent career.
snippet: For the 12 years that George Bush held national elective office, Jeb Bush used his unique access to seek favors and make suggestions, helping bolster his own nascent career.
lead_paragraph: The stream of requests to the White House from Jeb Bush, a young but well-connected Republican leader in South Florida, ranged from the weighty and urgent to the parochial and mundane.

abstract: A city long overshadowed by nearby New York and Washington has learned to take pride in the creativity born of its relative affordability.
snippet: A city long overshadowed by nearby New York and Washington has learned to take pride in the creativity born of its relative affordability.
lead_paragraph: PHILADELPHIA — Cheesesteaks? Never mind. Sichuan shoestring French fries? That’s more like it. Like many American cities, Philadelphia has greatly evolved both economically and culturally since 2000, the last time a major political party held its national convention here, not to mention the days when W. C. Fields made it a national punch line.

abstract: The 57th annual Grammy Awards packed 23 performances around nine awards presentations.
snippet: The 57th annual Grammy Awards packed 23 performances around nine awards presentations.
lead_paragraph: For a singer who received a near-coronation — from best new artist to song of the year — Sam Smith played it modest at the 57th annual Grammy Awards, broadcast on Sunday night from the Staples Center in Los Angeles.
